    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25789833_19_13521-13612",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "13521-13612",
      "markText": "你们应当知道，一切众生，从无始以来，一直在六道中轮回，在生死中流转，都因为不知常住真心，这是吾人本具的清净光明之性体，却沉迷于妄想分别之中，导致种种虚妄假相并误以为真，故有轮回流转。",
      "totalCount": 476,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25789833&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=13521&rangeEnd=13612",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b932b60718985899b9de18?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=13521&rangeEnd=13612"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25789833_20_14738-14805",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "14738-14805",
