      "totalCount": 465,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25789833&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=14738&rangeEnd=14805",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b932b60718985899b9de18?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=14738&rangeEnd=14805"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25789833_20_16556-16624",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "16556-16624",
      "markText": "一切众生从无始来，迷己为物，失于本心，为物所转，故于是中，观大观小。若能转物，则同如来，身心圆明，不动道场，于一毛端遍能含受十方国土。”",
      "totalCount": 459,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25789833&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=16556&rangeEnd=16624",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b932b60718985899b9de18?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=16556&rangeEnd=16624"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25789833_20_24777-24870",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "24777-24870",
      "markText": "你应当了知，这精觉妙明的见性，非是因生，非是缘生，也非是自然而有；也不能说不是因缘，或不是自然；本没有非与不非，也没有是与非是；它出离一切妄情计度之相，又圆融一切法，全体法界，不一不异。",
      "totalCount": 448,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25789833&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=24777&rangeEnd=24870",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b932b60718985899b9de18?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=24777&rangeEnd=24870"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25789833_19_1286-1307",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "1286-1307",
      "markText": "阿难遭魔的原因是由一向求多闻而未能实修禅定",
      "totalCount": 434,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25789833&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=1286&rangeEnd=1307",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b932b60718985899b9de18?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=1286&rangeEnd=1307"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25789833_19_32385-32464",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "32385-32464",
      "markText": "如果离开现前六尘境相而仍有分别觉知之性，即真正是你的心；然而，如果分别觉知之性，离开六尘境相就没有体性了，那它不过是现前六尘的分别尘影之事，是虚幻而不是真心。",
      "totalCount": 420,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25789833&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=32385&rangeEnd=32464",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b932b60718985899b9de18?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=32385&rangeEnd=32464"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25789833_19_35145-35181",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "35145-35181",
      "markText": "是故当知，灯能显色，如是见者，是眼非灯；眼能显色，如是见性，是心非眼。”",
      "totalCount": 405,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25789833&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=35145&rangeEnd=35181",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b932b60718985899b9de18?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=35145&rangeEnd=35181"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25789833_20_8727-8775",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "8727-8775",
      "markText": "殊不知，这个五蕴色身，乃至色身之外的一切山河虚空大地，皆是妙明真心中所现之物，无一超出自心之外。",
      "totalCount": 405,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25789833&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=8727&rangeEnd=8775",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b932b60718985899b9de18?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=8727&rangeEnd=8775"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25789833_19_16184-16226",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "16184-16226",
      "markText": "若是你的灵明之心实在身内，就应先能了知身内；可有哪个人是先见身内之物，后见身外之物？",
      "totalCount": 360,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25789833&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=16184&rangeEnd=16226",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b932b60718985899b9de18?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=16184&rangeEnd=16226"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25789833_19_1586-1629",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "1586-1629",
      "markText": "一切众生从无始来，生死相续，皆由不知常住真心，性净明体，用诸妄想，此想不真，故有轮转”",
      "totalCount": 342,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25789833&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=1586&rangeEnd=1629",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b932b60718985899b9de18?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=1586&rangeEnd=1629"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25789833_19_20436-20455",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "20436-20455",
      "markText": "由心生故，种种法生，由法生故，种种心生",
      "totalCount": 336,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25789833&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=20436&rangeEnd=20455",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b932b60718985899b9de18?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=20436&rangeEnd=20455"
    },
    {
